  56:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off  8-11 BE int32: Altitude  scale 1000
  57:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off 12-13 BE int16: Gnd speed scale 100
  58:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off 14-15 BE int16: Heading   scale 10
  59:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off 16-17 BE int16: HACC      scale 100
  60:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off 18-19 BE int16: VACC      scale 100
  61:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off 20-21 BE int16: SACC      scale 100
