 171:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off  4   uint8:    CPU %
 172:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off  5-6 BE int16: Status flags
 173:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off  7-8 BE int16: Time              scale 1   (s)
 174:movi_comm.c   ****  *   off  9-10 BE int16: Pressure         scale 10  (984.0mb confirmed)
